### Add a TEXT content item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}/content-items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "type": "TEXT",
  "title": "Introduction to Bornean Biodiversity",
  "textContent": "<p>Borneo is home to over 15,000 plant species.</p>",
  "order": 1
}

###

### Add a VIDEO content item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}/content-items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "type": "VIDEO",
  "title": "Field Identification Techniques",
  "videoSource": "YOUTUBE",
  "videoUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=example",
  "allowOffline": false,
  "order": 2
}

###

### List content items for a module
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}/content-items
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update a content item
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}/content-items/{{contentItemId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "title": "Updated Title"
}

###

### Reorder content items
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}/content-items/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "items": [
    { "id": "{{contentItemId}}", "order": 0 }
  ]
}

###

### Delete a content item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/modules/{{moduleId}}/content-items/{{contentItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
